        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You call forth a swirling storm of dust. The <em>dust storm</em> obscures vision, with the effect of <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Obscuring Mist]{Obscuring Mist}</em>. The dust also makes the air unbreathable; creatures in the area must hold their breath, though wearing a scarf or similar clothing over the mouth increases the time the creature can hold its breath to 5 rounds. Creatures entering or starting their turn in the <em>dust storm</em> take 1d6 slashing damage. Creatures that have the water trait or that are made primarily of liquid take double damage.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+2)</strong> The damage increases by 1d6.</p>"
